{"data":[{"name":"97:1","price":"本当にわれら*は、誉れの夜にそれ（クルアーン*）を下した。","arabic":"إِنَّآ أَنزَلۡنَٰهُ فِي لَيۡلَةِ ٱلۡقَدۡرِ","category":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr"],"ayahNumber":6126,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"innā anzalnāhu fī laylati al-qadri ","translations":["Indeed, We","revealed it","in","(the) Night","(of) Power","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["innā","anzalnāhu","fī","laylati","al-qadri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2949],[2,2949,5469],[3,5469,5939],[4,5939,6759],[5,6759,7884]]}},{"name":"97:2","price":"（預言者*よ、）誉れの夜が何かを、何があなたに知らせるのか？","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا لَيۡلَةُ ٱلۡقَدۡرِ","category":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr"],"ayahNumber":6127,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā laylatu al-qadri ","translations":["And what","can make you know","what","(the) Night","(of) Power (is)","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","laylatu","al-qadri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2130],[2,2130,3260],[3,3260,3670],[4,3670,4480],[5,4480,5945]]}},{"name":"97:3","price":"誉れの夜は、千の月に優るもの。¹","arabic":"لَيۡلَةُ ٱلۡقَدۡرِ خَيۡرٞ مِّنۡ أَلۡفِ شَهۡرٖ","category":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr"],"ayahNumber":6128,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　つまり、そこにおける正しい行い*は、誉れの夜がない千の月における正しい行い*に優る、ということ（ムヤッサル５９８頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"laylatu al-qadri khayrun min alfi shahrin ","translations":["(The) Night","(of) Power","(is) better","than","a thousand","month(s)","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["laylatu","al-qadri","khayrun","min","alfi","shahrin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1700],[3,1700,2380],[4,2380,3740],[5,3740,4300],[6,4300,5465]]}},{"name":"97:4","price":"天使*たちと魂（ジブリール*）¹はそこにおいて、彼らの主*のお許しと共に、（かれがお定めになった）全ての物事ゆえ、次々と降臨する。²","arabic":"تَنَزَّلُ ٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ وَٱلرُّوحُ فِيهَا بِإِذۡنِ رَبِّهِم مِّن كُلِّ أَمۡرٖ","category":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr"],"ayahNumber":6129,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　ここでジブリール*が「魂」と呼ばれていることについては、マルヤム*章１７の訳注を参照。 ２　煙霧章４の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"tanazzalu al-malāikatu wal-rūḥu fīhā bi-idh'ni rabbihim min kulli amrin ","translations":["Descend","the Angels","and the Spirit","therein","by (the) permission","(of) their Lord","for","every","affair","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["tanazzalu","al-malāikatu","wal-rūḥu","fīhā","bi-idh'ni","rabbihim","min","kulli","amrin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1030],[2,1030,4070],[3,4070,5000],[4,5000,5900],[5,5900,6600],[6,6600,7610],[7,7610,9520],[8,9520,10110],[9,10110,10715]]}},{"name":"97:5","price":"黎明の出現まで、それは（いかなる悪からも、）まさしく安全¹なのである。","arabic":"سَلَٰمٌ هِيَ حَتَّىٰ مَطۡلَعِ ٱلۡفَجۡرِ","category":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr"],"ayahNumber":6130,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「安全（サラーム）」という語は、「『平安を』という、天使*たちの挨拶（家畜章５４の訳注を参照）」のことである、という解釈もある（アル＝バガウィー５：２８９参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"salāmun hiya ḥattā maṭlaʿi al-fajri ","translations":["Peace","it (is)","until","(the) emergence","(of) the dawn","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["salāmun","hiya","ḥattā","maṭlaʿi","al-fajri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,1580],[3,1580,2480],[4,2480,3390],[5,3390,5085]]}}],"chapter":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr","Chapter Al-Qadr","Qadr","Surah Qadr","Chapter Qadr","Al Qadr","Surah Al Qadr","Chapter Al Qadr","Surah 97","Chapter 97","The Power","القدر"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}